race.description: Guyra Fuels / Fourways Service Centre Maiden Handicap
race.comment: NAFTALI (2) in need of the run first-up over the shorter trip when a plugging eighth over 1200m at Scone. Maps well again and expected to go close out to the 1400m. RUFUS ATTICUS (7) total forgive in the heavy conditions when a battling sixth over 1420m at Grafton. Earlier efforts had merit and near his top for this on the good surface. NAVY BUOY (1) consistent gelding who resumes for the Paul Snowden yard and shouldn't be a maiden for long. Stretched out to the 2000m when a tough third over 2000m at Kembla last June. Fitted with the one trial placing over 1006m at Port Macquarie. Expected to sprint well fresh. ZOUGO BOSS (9) back in trip on the backup and not without each-way claims.
